data.description: SELLER WILL PAY $5,000 BUYER’S CLOSING COSTS! This property has 5 bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms, which provide ample space & convenience for daily use & accommodating guests. The home is an open floor plan, which creates a sense of space & facilitates easy flow between living areas. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances & granite counter tops which are both durable & visibly appealing as well as easy to maintain. In the kitchen, there is a pantry providing extra storage space for groceries & kitchen supplies. The property has lots of attic space with partial flooring. This additional space can be used for storage or potentially finished for other purposes. There is an 11'9x12'5 covered porch, which can be a great place to relax & enjoy the outdoors while being protected from the elements. A 12'5x23 extended patio area is also available. This space can be used for outdoor dining, entertaining, or simply enjoying the outdoor environment.
